description:
This market will resolve to “Over” if the jersey number of the first player to score a touchdown in Super Bowl LX is 20 or higher.

This market will resolve to “Under” if the jersey number of the first player to score a touchdown in Super Bowl LX is 19 or lower.

If no touchdown is scored during Super Bowl LX, this market will resolve to 50-50.

If no single player is officially credited with the first touchdown of Super Bowl LX, this market will resolve to 50-50.

If Super Bowl LX is cancelled or postponed beyond February 22, 2026 at 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the NFL; however, a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
